columns:

`$.GRanges`   = function( x, name )        {
  if( name %in% c( 'seqnames', 'ranges', 'strand' ) ) {
    do.call( name, list( x ) )
  }
  else {
    elementMetadata( x )[[ name ]]
  }
}

Sorry about that (it's amazing what you see as soon as you click 'send')


Cheers,

Tim Yates

